SMS,Central,provides,users,with,an,online,SMS,portal,for,launching,bulk,SMS,campaigns,and,sending,two,way,SMS,It,also,allows,users,to,personalize,messages,for,their,recipients,customize,sender,ID,create,templates,schedule,campaigns,for,a,later,time,and,date,and,review,previous,messages,and,their,metrics,Users,can,also,send,SMS,by,email,or,API,The,SMS,Central,API,allows,users,to,integrate,with,its,messaging,gateway,using,REST,or,SMPP,calls